sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as AirBar / Network App
    participant KS as connectivityStore
    participant KC as kernelClient
    participant KR as Kernel (device.js)
    participant SV as connectivityService.js

    Note over UI,SV: WiFi Scan
    UI->>KS: refresh()
    KS->>KC: request("device.connectivity.status")
    KC->>KR: route -> handle
    KR->>SV: getStatus()
    SV->>SV: networksetup -getairportpower
    SV->>SV: system_profiler SPAirPortDataType
    SV-->>KR: {wifiEnabled, networks[], currentNetworkLabel}
    KR-->>KC: response
    KC-->>KS: patch state
    KS-->>UI: re-render

    Note over UI,SV: WiFi Connect
    UI->>KS: connectNetwork(ssid, password?)
    KS->>KC: request("device.wifi.connect", {ssid, password})
    KC->>KR: route -> handle
    KR->>SV: connectWifi(ssid, password)
    SV->>SV: networksetup -setairportnetwork "Wi-Fi" ssid
    SV-->>KR: updated status
    KR-->>KC: response
    KC-->>KS: patch state
    KS-->>UI: re-render
